  "response": "Attraction and relationships are complex and influenced by many factors beyond physical appearance. While some people might perceive that attractive individuals receive more attention or have higher standards, this is not a universal rule. Each person has unique preferences and values, and what one person finds attractive may differ for another.\n\nAdditionally, the dynamics of relationships and attraction are also shaped by personality, interests, compatibility, and other traits that go beyond looks. Some people might find it easier to connect with individuals who share similar interests or values, regardless of their appearance.\n\nIt's important to approach relationships with respect, understanding, and an open mind, recognizing that everyone is different and has their own unique experiences and expectations.",
